rows.label: qst00100103_msg0001
rows.name:
Ah! Thanks a lot, Gegebi pass
watch duty to Limuli no problemo!

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0002
rows.name:
Limuli smash previous lateness record
of 7,691 seconds.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0003
rows.name:
Because this happen thousandth time,
Gegebi plan to lecture him for three
days and three nights.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0004
rows.name:
But Limuli gave Gegebi half of
delicious Cinnopon Roll, so
Gegebi forgive him.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0005
rows.name:
Gegebi not monster. Generosity of
Gegebi wide as Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0007
rows.name: Here is reward from generous Gegebi.

rows.label: qst00100103_msg0008
rows.name:
If you see suspicious activity
aboard Goldmund, please report
to Gegebi or Limuli!
